Dia. 01 6 Points
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Let's check \b A\b0 .
\par If Black plays at 1, Black's territory doesn't increase.
\par If White plays, he makes \cf1\b 6 points\cf0\b0  by capturing 3 stones.
\par
\par Therefore this move is worth 6 points for both players and it is counted with the simple counting method.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
